<i>noun</i>: 연루 [열루], 결탁 [결탁], 가담 [가담] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>연루 [열루]</dt><br>
<dd>complicity</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람이 저지른 범죄에 관련됨.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being involved in a crime committed by someone.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>결탁 [결탁]</dt><br>
<dd>collusion; conspiracy; complicity</dd><br>
<dd>주로 나쁜 일을 꾸미려고 서로 짜고 도움을 주고받음.</dd><br>
<dd>Helping each other in a conspiracy, usually in plotting something bad.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>가담 [가담]</dt><br>
<dd>participation; involvement; complicity</dd><br>
<dd>한편이 되어 일을 하거나 도움.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of joining a team or a group to help or to work together.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>